<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Json::decode doesn't throw an exception on failure.</p>

<p>Additionally the return value of json_decode has changed on invalid data within ZF supported php versions:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
var_dump(json_decode('invalid json'));
// -&gt; NULL
</code></pre>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
var_dump(json_decode('invalid json'));
// -&gt; string(16) "invalid json"
</code></pre>

    </div>
